              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "The GEANIE spectrometer consists of 26 HPGe",
                "detectors, 20 of which haveBGO active shields. Of",
                "the 26 Ge detectors, 16 are coaxial geometry with a",
                "dynamic range up to 4 MeV and 10 are planar geometry",
                "detectors with a limited dynamic range of 1 MeV.",
                "Only coaxial detectors were used in the experiment."
              ]
